# Math Worksheets Generator

A web-based tool for generating printable math worksheets as PDFs.

The application lets you define allowed values, operators, and constraints, then generates one or more worksheet pages with optional answer keys. It is designed to be simple, fast, and usable on both desktop and mobile browsers.

Live site (when deployed):
https://mathworksheets.se

---

## Features

- Generate worksheets as PDF
- 3 columns × 20 problems per page (60 per page)
- Optional answers page after each worksheet
- Supports multiple pages (worksheet + answers per page set)
- Operators:
  - +, -, *, /
  - •, ×, ÷
- Flexible number input:
  - Ranges: 0-10, -10--5
  - Lists: 1 3 5, 6-10, 100, -99
  - Decimals: .1 .25 3.5
- Optional constraints:
  - Non-negative subtraction results
  - Integer-only division results
- Monospaced (Courier) layout, print-friendly
- Automatic fallback to defaults if inputs are invalid

---

## How It Works

1. Open the website in your browser
2. Fill in the form:
   - Allowed values for a and b
   - Operators
   - Number of pages
   - Optional constraints
3. Click “Generate PDF”
4. A PDF is generated server-side and downloaded to your computer

No data is stored.

---

## Input Format

### Allowed values for a / b

You can combine ranges and explicit values.

Examples:

0-10
-10--5
1 3 5
6-10, 100, -99
.1 .2 .5 1.25

Notes:
- Ranges must use integer endpoints
- Values can be separated by spaces and/or commas
- Invalid input falls back to defaults automatically

---

### Operators

Supported operators:

+  -  *  /  •  ×  ÷

Examples:

+
+-×÷
+,-,•,×,÷
+++++-/*

Repeated operators act as weights (e.g. “+++++-/*” favors addition).

---

### Pages

- Each page contains 60 problems
- If “answers” is checked:
  - Each worksheet page is followed by its answers page
- Maximum pages: 200
  - With answers enabled → up to 400 PDF pages

---

## PDF Layout

- Header: custom text (Courier)
- Footer:
  - Left: current date
  - Right: page number
- Problems and answers are monospaced and aligned for printing

