## Tech Stack

- Python
- Flask
- ReportLab (PDF generation)
- Gunicorn (production server)
- Render (hosting)

---

## Local Development

Requirements:

Python 3.10+

Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt

Run locally:

python app.py

Open in browser:

http://127.0.0.1:5000

---

## Deployment (Render)

The app is designed to be deployed as a Render Web Service.

Render configuration:

Build command:
pip install -r requirements.txt

Start command:
gunicorn app:app

Custom domain and HTTPS are handled by Render.

